OL,5, Lawyers for the man who admitted to    
OL,6, stealing ruby slippers worn in The     
OL,7, Wizard of Oz have finally revealed his 
OL,8, motive in a sentencing memo.           
OL,10,FTerry Jon Martin, 76, had given up his 
OL,11,Flife of crime but wanted to make "one  
OL,12,Flast score", according to the memo.    
OL,14,FAn old mob associate convinced him to  
OL,15,Fcarry out the smash-and-grab heist in  
OL,16,F2005.                                  
OL,18,FHe was caught more than a decade later 
OL,19,Fwhen an FBI art crime team recovered   
OL,20,Fthe slippers in a sting operation.     
